definition: Beibei district of central Chongqing municipality, formerly in Sichuan

sentences.english: Part four study the development mode of Urban Eco-agriculture in Beibei.
sentences.chinese: 北碚區都市生態農業發展模式研究。

sentences.english: The present measures shall be interpreted by the Investment Promotion Bureau of Beibei District together with relevant departments.
sentences.chinese: 本辦法由北碚區招商局會同有關部門負責解釋。

sentences.english: Among the Five Friendlies, Beibei is known to be gentle and pure.
sentences.chinese: 其中5友誼賽，北碚區是衆所周知的溫柔和純潔性。

sentences.english: Part five put forward the countermeasure and arrangement guaranteed system of the development of Urban Eco-agriculture in Beibei.
sentences.chinese: 提出北碚區發展都市生態農業的對策措施保障體系。
